            . This Deponent being asked how much Money the Prisoner confest he stole from the Prosecutor, said, about a Guinea, being told the Indictment mentioned but 10 s. and 8 d. he said he believed it was but Half a Guinea; being asked how much Half a Guinea was? he said 12 s. The Prisoner, having about as much Sense as the Prosecutor and his Evidence, said in his Defence, that he being in a Mind for Gaming, went and pawned his Coat for Money, and meeting Dick Lyn, they sell to it, and he won 
