               <p>N. B. The Reasons for writing this Trial directly as it was spoke, is, that others may provide themselves with proper Terms of Speech before they appear at such a Court of Judicature, and not to please the vulgar Part of the Town with Buffoonry, this not being a Paper of Entertainment.</p>
